riginal_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.2258,"vote_count":23191,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/o3i6AfTcWAuNvzAUV3q5lOmi6Gx.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"},{"id":527774,"adult":false,"title":"Raya and the Last Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Long ago, in the fantasy world of Kumandra, humans and dragons lived together in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.6169,"vote_count":7181,"poster_path":"/5nVhgCzxKbK47OLIKxCR1syulOn.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-03","vote_average":7.803,"backdrop_path":"/zmX7ObPaRfiCmY6LMalUb1bJDKj.jpg","original_title":"Raya and the Last Dragon","original_language":"en"},{"id":468224,"adult":false,"title":"Tolkien","video":false,"overview":"England, early 20th century. The future writer and philologist John Ronald Reuel Tolkien (1892-1973) and three of his schoolmates create a strong bond between them as they share the same passion for literature and art, a true fellowship that strengthens as they grow up, but the outbreak of World War I threatens to shatter it.","genre_ids":[10752,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3956,"vote_count":1516,"poster_path":"/A7eYO3t7oZQdfJj5KlJBI7GhT9H.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-0